Show or hide names in thumbnail videos in meetings, webinars, and events
In Webex Meetings, Webex Webinars, and Webex Events (classic), choose how you want the names of participants to appear. If you don't know everyone, show everyone's names all the time to help you learn them. Hide participant names if want focus on their video more clearly.
Desktop
iPhone, Android phone
iPad, Android tablet
Web
1
During a meeting, click Layout .
2
Select Names in videos and then choose one of the following options:
Automatically hide names when not speaking—Default option that keeps names hidden until the participant speaks.
Show all names—Shows participant names always.
Hide all names—Hides participant names except for when you hover over their video.